      <h1>CORONAVIRUS</h1>
      <h5>Coronavirus disease is an infectious disease caused by a new virus called the COVID-19. The disease causes respiratory illness (like the flu) with symptoms such as a cough, fever, and in more severe cases, difficulty of breathing. As of now, there is no proper cure/vaccine for this disease. The first case in Bangladesh was confirmed on 7 March 2020 by the IEDCR. Considering the health system, Bangladesh is currently at a very high risk of probable nationwide spread of the virus.</h5>
    </div>

