            <h2>Mortality Rate is 3.4%</h2>
            <p>Globally, about 3.4% of reported COVID-19 cases have died. By comparison, seasonal flu generally kills far fewer than 1% of those infected. [As of 3 March 2020]</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
